     H            Y.
     F** AIAR54 **************************************
     F* ..通信ＰＣ　送受信コントロールプログラム.. *
     F*      A.MAMIYA                2004.08.11      *
     F************************************** AIAR54 **
     FOUTPUT  O   F     256            DISK
     C*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PSTS    1
     C                     PARM           PREC   100
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDPREC      WREC   100
     C                     Z-ADD0         WSIZE  100
     C*
     C           WREC      IFEQ 0
     C                     MOVEL'E'       PSTS
     C                     ELSE
     C           WREC      MULT 1024      WSIZE
     C                     EXCPTDT
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PSTS
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     OOUTPUT  E                DT
     O                         WSIZE     10
